                "invention-title": [
                    "Spreading type ocean energy hydrogen production platform",
                    "铺展式海波能制氢平台"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a spreading type sea wave energy hydrogen production platform which comprises a platform body, the platform body comprises a sea wave energy power generation unit, the electric energy output end of the sea wave energy power generation unit is connected with a power distribution room, and the power distribution room is connected with a sea water desalination system through a cable; the seawater desalination system comprises an electromagnetic distillation pressure furnace and a heat recovery cone-pot steam turbine. According to the spreading type sea wave energy hydrogen production platform, electric energy generated by sea waves is utilized to distill seawater into drinkable water and can also be used for hydrogen production, the efficiency of converting non-waste heat energy into mechanical energy is improved, and the waste heat recovery difficulty is reduced."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种铺展式海波能制氢平台，包括平台主体，平台主体包括海波能发电单元，海波能发电单元的电能输出端连接有配电房，配电房通过电缆与海水淡化系统连接；海水淡化系统包括电磁蒸馏压力炉、热回收锥壶汽轮机。本发明提供的铺展式海波能制氢平台，利用海波产生的电能将海水蒸馏成可饮用水的同时还能用于制氢，而且提高了非余热能量转化为机械能的效率，降低对余热回收的难度。"
                }
            ]
